<D>__{he's giving us a blank check on wiretaps. so i've set 'em up on all of juno's shipping agents, her clients, and faisil made up a list of possible contacts that crimson jihad might have in this country. now all we can do is wait }
<A>__{he notices harry is not listening.}
<C>__{gib}
<D>__{is this national security stuff boring you?}
